Place cereal on waxed paper. Whisk eggs, orange peel, orange juice, granulated sugar and vanilla in shallow dish until well blended. Dip bread slices into orange juice mixture; coat lightly with cereal. Melt 1 Tbsp. margarine in large skillet over medium heat. Add bread slices in batches to skillet; cook until browned on both sides, adding more margarine as needed. Sprinkle with powdered sugar.